Summary: Transparent object with radar detection only
divs: Sighting DetailsNews report reported a large object in the sky that they could not identify. Itwas invisible, but it did have a radar bounce, they checked radar for precip andthere was none.Initally they reported the object over the Dakotas moving into Minnesota. duringthee broad cast. Throughout the broadcast it was brought up how unusual thiswas.When the 6 Oclock news came on nothing at all was mentioned. Evening news samething, not a single channel mentioned it. This was very strange with how muchthe 5 oclock news had made such a big deal about this.Up to this time, the invisible mothership is still in orbit and still can betracked on radar.I was hoping to find a way to get more info about this, Im kinda excited.Diane Hinkley
